## developer tools

gestures:
- apple's gestures API, and polyfills
- http://dev.sencha.com/deploy/touch/examples/kitchensink/
- show graphic of images

simulate events:
- phantom limb for single touch
- multitouch on laptop via MagicTouch.js
- remote debugging super useful (so far just PlayBook)

